{"tid":1048482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"作為男人嘅壓力係女人唔會明","createTime":"2019-03-05T16:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T17:41:55.000Z","uid":236682,"like":24,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"216721c25dffc56972774d6e1a63911a73195b2c","tid":1048482,"uid":236682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:18:56.000Z","msg":"屋企老豆老母日嘈夜嘈<br />\n幾廿歲人先話嗌離婚<br />\n老豆又唔生性响wechat識大陸雞<br />\n<br />\n事業已經可以話冇乜<br />\n俾人磨撚到無哂鋭氣<br />\n撞正個仆街老細 同事又個個唔撚幫手<br />\n想轉工又未搵得啱<br />\n<br />\n條女話要結婚 唔結就分<br />\n咁我都好愛佢<br />\n但諗深層 唔結就分 咁係為結婚而結婚定真係愛？<br />\n我唔明 不過都應承咗 年尾就註冊擺酒<br />\n之後又要搬一齊住 乜都係錢 乜都要諗<br />\n<br />\n其實我真係好撚攰"},{"pid":"5558250deaf9c0a3add71f7d9dc1402af461c378","tid":1048482,"uid":118647,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:23:47.000Z","msg":"你啫，你啲壓力男女都有機會有既啦，我就好彩啲，屋企人暫時都生生性性"},{"pid":"fceb0d2bc68d48f6f4636dc9d5b22c0f50978872","tid":1048482,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"請保重"},{"pid":"07cd4d7887d7a79e4b99c733cd6a6c49fec923be","tid":1048482,"uid":141782,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"呢d 野夠會發生女人身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c7fa0a60dbbbff1c484707f7f5f773e0344fc0","tid":1048482,"uid":236682,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"07cd4d7887d7a79e4b99c733cd6a6c49fec923be","tid":1048482,"uid":141782,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"呢d 野夠會發生女人身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"我無乜女仔朋友<br />\n所以好少聽女人會俾人講唔結婚就分手<br />\n<br />\n相反身邊好多男人被逼婚例子"},{"pid":"d32be923b8aaed379369b20c85f4e6c33a3864d8","tid":1048482,"uid":236682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fceb0d2bc68d48f6f4636dc9d5b22c0f50978872","tid":1048482,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re